You have got everything to take the world in your stride! So now go out there and celebrate this amazing spirit of womanhood with a grand Women's Day Special Buffet at The Raviz Kovalam. Great views of the Arabian Sea, caricature, mehendi, live band, complimentary cocktail / mocktail and a delectable spread @ 50% discount awaits for all womens at The Terrace.
